      "type": "METHOD_STEP",
      "text": "Heat the oven to 180C"
    },
    {
      "post_notes": [],
      "pre_notes": [],
      "type": "METHOD_STEP",
      "text": "Cut the aubergines into 6-7mm thick slices, then slice the cheese and tomato and season them with thyme, salt and pepper"
    },
    {
      "post_notes": [],
      "pre_notes": [],
      "type": "METHOD_STEP",
      "text": "Form the aubergine, cheese and tomato into \"sandwiches\" with the aubergine taking the part of the bread. Squish them a bit"
    },
    {
      "post_notes": [],
      "pre_notes": [],
      "type": "METHOD_STEP",
      "text": "Beat the eggs, brush on both sides and edges of the aubergine and dip the sandwiches in the breadcrumbs"
    },
    {
      "post_notes": [],
      "pre_notes": [],
      "type": "METHOD_STEP",
      "text": "Shallow fry in around half a centimeter of oil over high heat until golden brown on both sides, then place on a baking tray lined with baking paper and bake for another 7-10 minutes"
